messages.content: Welcome to the Official Minecraft Earth Discord server! We are now public 🎉
We made it past 1000 members! Thanks to everyone of you for this amazing milestone!

It wasn't that long ago that we excitedly noted that we'd grown past the 1,000 member mark. This past weekend we blew way past 9,000 (a while ago but who can pass up an over 9,000 joke) and are now past the 20,000 member mark! Way to go Earthlings! :earth2:

We've made a temporary Discord server specifically for Minecon Live! The server features both news leading up to the event and a live updates channel for updates during the event, both of which can be followed to have news and updates posted in your own servers! The invite link is:
https://discord.gg/minecon
We're super excited to invite you all to join in the next Developer Q&A on 9/18 @ 12-1PM PDT!  Stop by, hang out, and get those questions ready!

:party_potato: Happy New Year 2020  and welcome to the 2020s! It's been 7 months since Minecraft Earth's first announcement, and MCE early access is now available worldwide, continuing to be a must-have AR game for every Minecraft enthusiasts! Thanks to every one of you for being a part of this server and the Minecraft/Minecraft Earth community! Looking forward to an awesome 2020 for Minecraft Earth and its brother, Minecraft! Just keep tapping!

- Minecraft Earth Moderation Team

Wildlife Sanctuary Build Challenge! 🌳:muddy_pig::cluckshroom::horned_sheep:🌳

With Earth Day coming up, let’s pause for a second and appreciate our planet. In the same spirit, design and populate your own wildlife sanctuary with all the lively mobs and their variants in their safe habitat. Feel free to use as many or as few mob variants as you want and show off how you imagine these mobs in their safe habitat!

:timer: Challenge dates: April 14 – April 27

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.

Blocktastic mobs (and where to find them) Build Challenge! 💡 + 🖌️ = ❓

Cows with flowers! Snowmen with melon heads! Minecraft Earth is full of unique mobs, but what makes up the blocky DNA of our quirky friends? Imagination of course! Design your own unique mob that showcases your creativity and then build it! Use any and all blocks in your inventory to bring your creation to life. Is your mob big or small? Oink. It’s the #three-little-pigs-challenge! 
Build three different houses crafted from different materials: one should *include* hay bales, one should *include* wood planks, one should *include* bricks. Your house with bricks should look strong enough to withstand the big bad wolf’s huffing and puffing! Don’t forget to populate your houses with your three favorite pig mob variants (there’s plenty to choose from)! :spotted_pig:

:mc_heart: **Juneteenth Celebration**  :mc_heart:
We stand in support of the Black Community everywhere. On June 19th, Mojang Studios will be donating all profits from the digital storefront sales of Minecraft and Minecraft Dungeons, as well as purchases of content in the Minecraft Marketplace.

In addition to Mojang Studios commitment, us, the Minecraft Earth community, will be holding events throughout the day. 

For 24 hours we will be hosting a bunch of events from Build challenges to Giveaways! Our goal is to see the world united in care. Please feel free to join us in our myriad of events and win some Minecoins or copies of Minecraft Games!

**This is a totally community funded event and not sponsored by Mojang Studios in any way.** While participating in such events, remember to stay civil and follow #rules.

🕛 **Event Time:** 12:00AM PST to 11:59PM PST

For additional details, read about Mojang Studio’s initiative for the Juneteenth: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/supporting-black-community

Calling all explorers! Space probe MCE-R00 was launched on an adventure of the final frontier—space! The first satellite images reveal an unidentified spaceship. Unfortunately, the data was corrupted and the final appearance of the spaceship is unknown. Your build skills are needed to solve this exciting discovery!

:adventure_crystals: Custom Adventure Build Challenge! :adventure_crystals: 

Adventures! You’ve activated them to defeat mobs o’ plenty, mine epic treasure, and solve all the other wacky puzzles the game designers thought of. We know your minds are brimming with equally zany and  adventurey ideas and we want to see them in real life!

:adventures: How? **Design your own custom adventure!** Grab any size buildplate, use any and all blocks in your inventory, and place your favorite friendly or not-so friendly mobs.

Your creations should be just as fun in regular and life-size play modes. ↕️ Will you build high or low? 🧩 Puzzley contraptions? ⚔️ Hordes of mobs? 🆕 Something totally new? Now’s your time to shine—shine bright like an adventure crystal!
